{"body":[{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕組 搬運」\n（禁止在B站宣傳漫遊相關内容，否則拉黑）","location":2,"from":0,"to":3.1},{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕組 搬運」\n（禁止在B站宣傳漫遊相關内容，否則拉黑）\n（料理人）\n","location":2,"from":3.1,"to":5},{"content":"（料理人）\n","from":5,"location":2,"to":5.27},{"content":"（舞伎）\n","from":7.27,"location":2,"to":9.44},{"content":"（舞伎家的料理人）\n","from":9.44,"location":2,"to":17.99},{"content":"第一天會睡不著呢\n","from":90.69,"location":2,"to":93.78},{"content":"我也是\n","from":93.78,"location":2,"to":96.93},{"content":"今天是小堇第一次盤髮的日子\n","from":98.85,"location":2,"to":102.82},{"content":"（第4話 為了不眠之夜）\n","from":102.91,"location":2,"to":103.26},{"content":"會睡不著啊…\n（第4話 為了不眠之夜）\n","from":103.26,"location":2,"to":105.0},{"content":"（第4話 為了不眠之夜）\n","from":105.0,"location":2,"to":105.16},{"content":"好鬱悶啊\n（第4話 為了不眠之夜）\n","from":105.16,"location":2,"to":106.82},{"content":"（第4話 為了不眠之夜）\n","from":106.82,"location":2,"to":107.03},{"content":"好期待啊\n（第4話 為了不眠之夜）\n","from":107.03,"location":2,"to":108.52},{"content":"（第4話 為了不眠之夜）\n","from":108.52,"location":2,"to":108.79},{"content":"啊？\n","from":108.79,"location":2,"to":109.43},{"content":"會很漂亮吧…\n","from":109.73,"location":2,"to":111.77},{"content":"小堇盤起頭髮的樣子\n","from":111.77,"location":2,"to":114.27},{"content":"那麼  我出門了\n","from":117.75,"location":2,"to":119.53},{"content":"路上小心\n","from":119.53,"location":2,"to":121.13},{"content":"舞伎的髮髻都是真髮\n","from":121.84,"location":2,"to":124.72},{"content":"只有在每週一次重新盤髮的時候才會解開\n","from":125.4,"location":2,"to":129.3},{"content":"洗髮精也只有那時才可以用\n","from":129.88,"location":2,"to":132.19},{"content":"只要還是「舞伎」\n","from":133.17,"location":2,"to":134.86},{"content":"就必須從早到晚梳著髮髻生活\n","from":134.86,"location":2,"to":139.34},{"content":"那就…拜託您啦\n","from":157.31,"location":2,"to":161.02},{"content":"季代  肚子好餓啊\n","from":164.9,"location":2,"to":167.56},{"content":"我現在正在做晚餐哦\n","from":167.56,"location":2,"to":169.42},{"content":"太好了！\n","from":169.42,"location":2,"to":170.37},{"content":"晚餐是這個嗎？\n","from":170.89,"location":2,"to":172.62},{"c