"從今天起它就是小堇的枕頭了\n","from":278.8,"location":2,"to":280.89},{"content":"舞伎為了在睡覺時不弄亂髮髻\n","from":283.5,"location":2,"to":288.16},{"content":"會枕著方枕睡覺\n","from":288.16,"location":2,"to":289.76},{"content":"聽好了！\n","from":290.29,"location":2,"to":291.06},{"content":"要堅持下去哦！\n","from":291.06,"location":2,"to":292.15},{"content":"沒錯\n","from":292.15,"location":2,"to":293.05},{"content":"因為那是每個人都必須經歷的過程啊！\n","from":293.05,"location":2,"to":295.02},{"content":"忍一忍吧\n","from":295.02,"location":2,"to":296.36},{"content":"太可憐了…\n","from":297.4,"location":2,"to":298.96},{"content":"別哭了  姐姐\n","from":298.96,"location":2,"to":300.51},{"content":"太高了…\n","from":308.63,"location":2,"to":309.82},{"content":"喘不過氣  身體還會滑下去\n","from":309.82,"location":2,"to":313.27},{"content":"脖子都要斷了…\n","from":313.27,"location":2,"to":315.71},{"content":"肚子難受  手肘好痛…\n","from":315.71,"location":2,"to":318.59},{"content":"頭的重量全部堆到了臉頰上\n","from":318.93,"location":2,"to":322.02},{"content":"臉都麻了\n","from":322.02,"location":2,"to":323.04},{"content":"頭下面什麼都沒有不穩定…\n","from":323.04,"location":2,"to":325.99},{"content":"睡不著！！\n","from":327.56,"location":2,"to":328.84},{"content":"已經做好心理準備了\n","from":331.82,"location":2,"to":333.27},{"content":"但沒想到會這麼痛苦…\n","from":333.27,"location":2,"to":334.55},{"content":"但我是不會認輸的！\n","from":336.04,"location":2,"to":337.7},{"content":"不行  慘敗啊…\n","from":345.02,"location":2,"to":347.34},{"content":"怎麼辦才好…\n","from":348.05,"location":2,"to":349.81},{"content":"季代？\n","from":354.27,"location":2,"to":355.42},{"content":"你來啦！\n","from":356.3,"location":2,"to":357.45},{"content":"馬上就給你盛出來\n","from":358.22,"location":2,"to":359.49},{"content":"稍等一下哦  小堇\n","from":359.49,"location":2,"to":361.03},{"content":"因為我聽大家說第一天都會睡不著覺呢\n","from":363.19,"location":2,"to":366.85},{"content":"所以就做了一下\n","from":366.85,"location":2,"to":368.71},{"content":"（甜酒 （用大米和麯發酵後製作而成。如砂糖一般甜。））\n","from":369.01,"location":2,"to":371.54},{"content":"甜酒…\n（甜酒 （用大米和麯發酵後製作而成。如砂糖一般甜。））\n","from":371.54,"location":2,"to":373.27},{"content":"（甜酒 （用大米和麯發酵後製作而成。如砂糖一般甜。））\n","from":373.27,"location":2,"to":373.93},{"content":"我想肚子暖和起來的話就能睡得著了\n","from":374.3,"location":2,"to":377.31},{"content":"謝謝你啊  季代\n","from":383.83,"location":2,"to":386.33},{"content":"舞伎家的料理人\n（舞伎家的料理人）\n","from":392.37,"location":2,"to":395.8},{"content":"（舞伎家的料理人）\n","from":395.8,"location":2,"to":399.003},{"content":"堇和\n","from":400.27,"location":2,"to":401.43},{"content":"季代的\n","from":402.53,"location":2,"to":403.37},{"content":"（今日餐點）\n","from":403.71,"location":2,"to":405.51},{"content":"今日餐點\n（今日餐點）\n","from":405.51,"location":2,"to":406.95},{"content":"（今日餐點）\n","from":406.95,"location":2,"to":407.51},{"content":"今天的料理是甜酒\n","from":407.95,"location":2,"to":410.44},{"content":"大冬天喝的話身體會暖和起來呢\n","from":410.44,"location":2,"to":413.94},{"content":"過年的時候在神社會分發甜酒\n","from":413.94,"location":2,"to":416.35},{"content":"我經常喝呢\n","from":416.35,"location":2,"to":417.76},{"content":"我倒是挺喜歡的\n","from":417.76,"location":2,"to":419.22},{"content":"不過也有很多人討厭那股獨特的風味呢\n","from":419.22,"location":2,"to":422.68},{"content":"甜酒分為「用酒糟製作的甜酒」\n","from":422.95,"location":2,"to":426.13},{"content":"和「用米麯製作的甜酒」兩個種類呢\n","from":426.13,"location":2,"to":429.27},{"content":"味道和風味完全不同哦\n","from":429.27,"location":2,"to":431.9},{"content":"酒糟甜酒和米麯甜酒  製作的方法完全不同呢\n","from":433.72,"location":2,"to":438.37},{"content":"那個…\n","from":438.58,"location":2,"to":439.86},{"content":"酒糟製作的甜酒指的是\n","from":440.19,"location":2,"to":441.86},{"content":"在用水化開的酒糟裡加入砂糖  經過調味後的東西\n","from":441.86,"location":2,"to":447.24},{"content":"因為酒糟是日本酒的殘渣\n","from":447.47,"location":2,"to":447.63},{"content":"（酒糟）\n因為酒糟是日本酒的殘渣\n","from":447.63,"location":2,"to":450.18},{"content":"（酒糟）\n含有微量的酒精\n","from":450.18,"location":2,"to":452.55},{"content":"含有微量的酒精\n","from":452.55,"location":2,"to":452.81},{"content":"而用米麯製作的甜酒指的是\n","from":452.81,"location":2,"to":455.39},{"content":"將蒸熟的大米用米麯菌發酵後製成的東西\n","from":455.39,"location":2,"to":459.42},{"content":"因此裡面不含酒精\n","from":459.42,"location":2,"to":462.09},{"content":"既有自然的甜味口感也很好\n","from":462.09,"location":2,"to":464.34},{"content":"容易入口\n","from":464.34,"location":2,"to":465.57},{"content":"書上是這麼寫的\n","from":465.57,"location":2,"to":466.92},{"content":"討厭酒糟甜酒的人\n","from":467.09,"location":2,"to":470.09},{"content":"也會喜歡上米麯甜酒呢\n","from":470.09,"location":2,"to":473.36},{"content":"順便一提  只要有米麯的話\n","from":473.64,"location":2,"to":475.73},{"content":"在家也能製作甜酒哦\n","from":475.73,"location":2,"to":478.16},{"content":"話說回來季代\n","from":478.92,"location":2,"to":480.55},{"content":"我聽說你在用鍋子咕嘟咕嘟地煮大米\n","from":480.55,"location":2,"to":483.69},{"content":"那是為了讓它發酵然後製作甜酒是吧\n","from":483.69,"location":2,"to":487.01},{"content":"為了讓大米發酵\n","from":487.66,"location":2,"to":489.97},{"content":"要用毯子包裹住鍋子\n","from":489.97,"location":2,"to":491.87},{"content":"再用熱水袋進行保溫哦\n","from":491.87,"location":2,"to":493.89},{"content":"也有把鍋子放進泡沫塑膠製成的箱子裡\n","from":494.79,"location":2,"to":498.34},{"content":"進行保溫的方法呢\n","from":498.34,"location":2,"to":500.64},{"content":"泡沫塑膠是保溫性能很優秀的材質\n","from":501.01,"location":2,"to":504.66},{"content":"適合保持一定的溫度\n","from":504.66,"location":2,"to":508.59},{"content":"甜酒在家裡也能製作\n","from":508.59,"location":2,"to":511.6},{"content":"最近也有各式各樣的甜酒在銷售\n","from":511.6,"location":2,"to":515.08},{"content":"互相比較一下  找找自己喜歡的口味\n","from":515.08,"location":2,"to":517.83},{"content":"可能也是一件趣事哦\n","from":517.83,"location":2,"to":519.62},{"content":"（舞伎家的料理人）\n","from":519.957,"location":2,"to":524.962},{"content":"（第5話 一輩子不變的習慣）\n","from":524.96,"location":2,"to":528.42},{"content":"（鬆餅 （厚薄均勻 鬆鬆軟軟））\n","from":553.49,"location":2,"to":559.24},{"content":"好嘞\n","from":559.49,"location":2,"to":560.32},{"content":"季代  我來幫你上菜吧\n","from":560.32,"location":2,"to":563.2},{"content":"小堇\n","from":564.27,"location":2,"to":565.58},{"content":"謝謝你  麻煩了\n","from":565.58,"location":2,"to":567.49},{"content":"沒事\n","from":567.49,"location":2,"to":568.4},{"content":"反正坐著也靜不下來\n","from":568.4,"loc